FBIS4-36085 "drnes109_n_94011" FBIS-NES-94-109 Daily Report 6 Jun 1994 ISRAEL UK Embassy Expresses Concern Over Recent Violence UK Embassy Expresses Concern Over Recent Violence NC0606150394 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1300 GMT 6 Jun 94 NC0606150394 Beirut Radio Lebanon Arabic BFN [Text] The British Embassy in Beirut today expressed London's extreme concern over the recent escalation of violence in the south, particularly in the wake of the Israeli raid against a Hizballah center near Ba'labakk. The embassy emphasized Britain's position, which fully supports the implementation of UN Security Council Resolution 425, and called for the restoration of the Lebanese Government's effective authority over all Lebanese territory.
